parameters: 【Masamune】Huh... it's not moving.
【Masamune】 W-What is it!
【Sylvester von Weisshwaik】 Haa, haa, haa...

【Sylvester von Weisshwaik】 I am Sylvester von
Weisshwaik, a noble of the Kingdom of Prussia.

【Sylvester von Weisshwaik】 I've come to repel the
pervert.
【Skeleton Head】 What did you say!
【Masamune】 It's not like we...
【Masamune】 (I can't deny the perverted things!)

【Sylvester von Weisshwaik】 So you're a pervert
after all. I'll turn back right away.

【Sylvester von Weisshwaik】 Then I'll let it slide
this time.
【Skeleton Head】 ...Is that so?
【Sylvester von Weisshwaik】 What?

【Skeleton Head】 Is there something here that I
don't want to be seen?
【Masamune】 You...

【Sylvester von Weisshwaik】 T-There's nothing
here. But you should turn back!

【Sylvester von Weisshwaik】 This is my laboratory,
you see.

【Sylvester von Weisshwaik】 Listen. I've already
given you a warning. Don't expect another one.
【Leon】 What on earth was that?

【Leon】 Did they say there was a noble from the
Kingdom of Prussia? I wonder if such a person
exists.
【Tommy】 Hmm, I feel like I recognize that face.

【Skeleton Head】 Hehe, Masamune. It was just a
joke when I said I was going home earlier.

【Skeleton Head】 Let's go! We're going to search
for treasure!
【Masamune】 This person...

I hid a switch on the back of my personal memo
painting. Do not press it.
Someone's diary
I cannot forgive Photon Graphpad.

In some circles, they are revered as the founder
of voyeuristic magic, but they are just
criminals.

I always peek at girls changing, but I never
manage to gather any evidence.

Thanks to that, I have managed to escape from
Professor Hoffman's pursuit.

However, after various twists and turns, we have
successfully managed to expel him from the school.
His mistake probably made me serious.

I ended up getting involved with someone I should
never have gotten involved with.
However, the problem has not been resolved yet.
Is there anything I can do for Chachamaru...?

The password to activate the Memo Lever for
personal use is A cat has nine lives. By moving
the lever to the right, you can go from the center
to the left room.

【Masamune】 Whose diary is this with Chachamaru's
name on it?

【Tommy】 Seems like it belongs to an alumnus, but
maybe it's the diary of the person who created
this place.
【Tommy】 By the way, I wonder what happened?

【Masamune】 Does the name Photon Graphpard sound
familiar to you?
【Tommy】 Hmm, I wonder if there's anything...

【Masamune】 I still don't understand anything...
What's the plan, Skeleton Head?

【Skeleton Head】 If the person who wrote this
diary created this passage, it's quite
troublesome.
【Masamune】 Huh...

【Skeleton Head】 A person of justice like this
would never create a path that leads to the girls'
dormitory...
【Masamune】 ...
【Skeleton Head】 It's over... Let's go home.

【Masamune】 We know the password, so let's move
forward.
